::DarkMouse::

She gets back into the vent and crawls over to where BlackArachnia 
is.  She knows that the spider will set off the gas.  So she decided 
to take the spider with her.  She started to knaw through the vent 
and opened a large hole right above BlackArachnia's head.  If she 
turned on the gas, it would go to where she was and effect her too.
